{"tid":1943433,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"PlayStation係咪戇鳩?","createTime":"2020-03-25T16:29:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-26T01:58:46.000Z","uid":239674,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"de0f2ebe7c702c18e499d2c593e3604c0965b585","tid":1943433,"uid":239674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T16:29:30.000Z","msg":"大約三年前已經賣撚咗部ps4，竟然收到封咁既email<br />\n但係個address又係 PlayStation &lt;sony@email.sonyentertainmentnetwork.com&gt;<br />\n分唔到係咪spam<br />\n垃圾SONY CS得個電話冇得email reply<br />\n已經即刻改左PSN密碼<br />\nPSN亦都冇畀過其他人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n打機mic都冇開過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中間突然有簡體字係咪支那仔CS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申原文copy<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">注意 &ndash; 違反行為守則 <br />\n<br />\n!@#$%^&amp;*#$%@##$!@#!@，您好：<br />\n<br />\n您在信息的活動違反我們的使用條款。<br />\n<br />\n带有攻击或辱骂性质的内容，包括任何低俗言论、图像、音频、视频、其他用户生成的内容或针对他人的滥用内容。<br />\n<br />\n若再有任何違反行為，我們可能會暫停或永久禁用您的PlayStation Network帳戶或主機。<br />\n<br />\n我們希望所有玩家的行為都能遵照規定、尊重他人，並能設身處地為我們和其他玩家著想。在此提醒您了解我們對社群的行為期望，請在此處 查閱行為守則。<br />\n<br />\n謹致<br />\n<br />\nPlayStation&reg;安全團隊<br />\nSony Interactive Entertainment Asia<br />\n<a href=\"https://asia.playstation.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fasia.playstation.com%2F&d=8fAJgc%2Bq%2B0y88RV8Svjv4Z1e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=5872c14c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://asia.playstation.com/</a></span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"2b09c31af74064a83ee8ec90a8e564b2631f1efe","tid":1943433,"uid":239674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T16:32:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4468e033ec2b95f07b10353881dbc0eeef50189a","tid":1943433,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T16:36:30.000Z","msg":"我又係喎"},{"pid":"902ccb